S.FORM: Thyakan i Hsinchu a kuwan nu Kalinku ku niyazu' nu Thyakan. u kasalumaluma' nu Thyakan sa, 113 ku luma'. kumud nu kasabinawlan sa, 409 ku tademawan. kasabinawlan nu Ingcumin sa, 387 ku tademaw, pakalatu 95 . u zuma sa, cay ku Ingcumin, 22 ku tademaw, pakalatu 5 . u kasabinacadan, Tayal 89 , Amis 2 , Rukai 1 , zumazuma 2 . malalitin tu ihekalay atu zumaay a natinengan
